{"tid":2416218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華大化驗員毋需讀相關學科 　人工逾2.6萬蚊乜人都做得","createTime":"2021-02-21T00:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T06:09:35.000Z","uid":271829,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"190cb6b036411527832745881a1af15cf76cd0aa","tid":2416218,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T00:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xsLOIr9wPYCfApG_RjJ41TcOtqk=/395x415/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZUJGQXZTYNGLBEF7TF5GRMNNFI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxsLOIr9wPYCfApG_RjJ41TcOtqk%3D%2F395x415%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZUJGQXZTYNGLBEF7TF5GRMNNFI.JPG&h=6394dd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n隨着政府檢測計劃擴大，華大招聘化驗員的信息沒有間斷， 有員工向《蘋果》透露，由於化驗員的薪金豐厚，返夜更可賺取逾26,000元，而且學歷不拘，因此吸引來自五湖四海的人士見工上班，當中包括有剛畢業的新鮮人、保險從業員、跟車司機等，但由於缺乏相關經驗，不時錯漏百出，批評內部員工質素參差。<br />\n<br />\n在華大基因工作的阿松指，在公司工作的內地人和港人各佔一半，化驗員一般分兩更，朝9晚9及晚9朝9，每更12小時，早更的人工連同津貼約有18,000元，而夜更則大約有26,000元。由於薪金豐厚，加上不少人因疫情而失業，遂到華大基因應徵，「唔理你學歷係乜，總之喺interview時符合到佢要求都會請，入到去啲人學歷都好參差，有學生，中學生畢業都請，中年人，乜人都有，只要符合佢條件就請」。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210220/5TZK6ADX5VDZDOXWUIN5CSGLCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210220%2F5TZK6ADX5VDZDOXWUIN5CSGLCQ%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnaHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=776317e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210220%2F5TZK6ADX5VDZDOXWUIN5CSGLCQ%2F&h=adea8c13\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210220/5TZK6ADX5VDZDOXWUIN5CSGLCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"aa5c8d65f7bb7898d9306b88f31f1c7310ffe106","tid":2416218,"uid":356010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T00:05:52.000Z","msg":"乞食科最後救贖"},{"pid":"da4b00a68e21a6f5eefb7c524be85339